ock your sight. Thus, if\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1762,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/25\/allah-descends-last-third-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":14165,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tahajjud: Allah descends in the last third of the night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 25, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOur Lord Almighty descends to the lowest heaven in the last third of every night, saying: Who is calling upon Me that I may answer him? Who is asking from Me that I may give him?\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26124,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/26\/women-attend-fajr-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":14165,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fajr: Women attend dawn prayer with the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The believing women would pray the dawn prayer with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. Then, they would return home wrapped in their mantles; they would not be recognized by anyone. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 365, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 645 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0